lines: I love how these Xaela festival activities give me the chance to experience new things! Yes, yes. Back at Yuzuka Manor I only sorted jars, but look at me now! Sorting targets, sorting ropes, sorting thicker ropes...
Quite a few of our many, many attendees have come bearing gifts. Sorting through them all is hard on the fins, but fascinating. I can even taste the ones I think are food! I am sometimes wrong.
